Subject: EES Executive Committee and EES Operating Committee

Consistent with my message at the All Employee Meeting and in the interest of 
reducing hierarchies, flattening the organization and enfranchising our 
current and future leaders, I am pleased to annouce the members of each group.

Executive Committee

This group will meet regularly at least once a month to discuss core 
strategy, corporate policy and other strategic issues.  I will chair and lead 
this group.

Jeremy Blachman
Don Black
Wanda Curry
Scott Gahn
Sean Holmes
