Jim Steffes


Operating Committee

This group will meet at least weekly, including the Monday morning staff 
meeting (8:30 AM - 8C1), to discuss progress towards financial and 
non-financial objectives, business performance and other important tactical 
issues.  Janet Dietrich will chair and lead this group.

